Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.16,0:00:05.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,'非番'嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,'非番'好像在哪兒聽過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.75,0:00:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.21,0:00:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 是哪個啊 真名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.67,0:00:14.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.13,0:00:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.59,0:00:20.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們最近迷上了一部老片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.26,0:00:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙警察:比番
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.18,0:00:24.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開創了一個時代的特攝節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.14,0:00:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比番是宇宙警察'非番'的意思是休假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.94,0:00:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前一直都在警戒中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.53,0:00:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想讓大家輪流休假
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.26,0:02:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爲什麽會是溫泉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.56,0:02:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微動用了一點關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.35,0:02:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉旅館嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.44,0:02:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還沒住過呢 真期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.73,0:02:25.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附近好像還有一個滑雪場哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.61,0:02:28.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎 我好想試試滑雪板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.19,0:02:32.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 一起去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.41,0:02:36.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不去滑雪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.41,0:02:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還有別的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.29,0:02:43.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.17,0:02:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.59,0:02:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山尻浩史探險隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在未開發的雪山上發現雪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.47,0:02:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.97,0:02:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的探險綜藝節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.64,0:02:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這個探險小隊打算前往雪山尋找雪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.62,0:03:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害 居然訂到這麽好的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.37,0:03:24.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微動用了一點關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.50,0:03:25.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是悠水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.25,0:03:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Altai·Torte的第一次旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要留下美好的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.63,0:03:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說的是啊 謝了 悠水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.93,0:03:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們快去找雪人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.23,0:03:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這必要用這麽專業的裝備嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.02,0:03:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是探險啊 這點程度不是很正常嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真名說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.12,0:04:07.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 真名她們還真是認真啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定真能找到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.63,0:04:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.05,0:04:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那樣也很有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.51,0:04:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們菜森真名探險隊爲了尋找未知生物雪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.56,0:04:26.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來到了大雪覆蓋的深山之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪人親~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.40,0:04:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊長突然開始呼喚雪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像是在搜尋遇難者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.07,0:04:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不會欺負你的 快出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.95,0:04:40.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 在搜索離家出走的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.95,0:04:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿芽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.08,0:04:47.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初學者一上來就從這裏開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.71,0:04:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是難度有點高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.42,0:04:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 已經好好預習過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.96,0:04:56.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先在山腹把滑雪板立起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.80,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿芽 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.81,0:05:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.85,0:05:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們追尋著雪人來到雪山深處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.07,0:05:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仍舊沒有發現雪人的蹤跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.32,0:05:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就在這時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.61,0:05:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.03,0:05:20.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真名隊長的聲音突然響起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.28,0:05:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到底能解開未知生物的謎團嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.83,0:05:31.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔細一看 似乎是兔子的足跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是還不能大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.59,0:05:36.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也存在是小雪人的可能性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.09,0:05:39.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真名隊長突然提出新的想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.63,0:05:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 快找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,循著脚印跑了起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.60,0:05:46.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這串脚印到底通向何方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.27,0:05:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這什麽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.11,0:05:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有啊 巨大的雪人脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.28,0:06:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那大概是熊的脚印 很危險的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.20,0:06:06.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的 怎麽看都不是熊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.83,0:06:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麽了悠水 這麽興奮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.75,0:06:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因爲你看 沒想到真的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 好過分 是真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.34,0:06:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 不過現在百分百確信了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.01,0:06:19.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.76,0:06:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也變得興奮起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.01,0:06:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真的存在的話 肯定早就發現了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.97,0:06:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能性是有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.57,0:06:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爲了替換你們 我們明晚就回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.91,0:06:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能 是什麽意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.16,0:06:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能說明一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.62,0:06:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 不小心聽到你們談話就插了進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.41,0:06:56.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪枝對七大不可思議之類的未解之謎很瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.84,0:07:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們剛剛說的是關於UMA的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.30,0:07:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,UMA是Unidentified Mysterious Animal的縮寫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.43,0:07:09.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是未知生物的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.56,0:07:13.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於UMA 包括謠傳和可信度高的生物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.23,0:07:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界各地都時有報道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.02,0:07:26.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個地區也多次出現關於雪人傳說的目擊和野生動物出沒的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.12,0:07:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你們發現的脚印不是熊的可能性很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.34,0:07:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二穗也相信雪人嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.55,0:07:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是相信雪枝而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.09,0:07:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二穗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.43,0:07:52.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且作爲本滑雪場的招牌 多種雪人的商品已經投產了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有的話會拉低銷量的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.40,0:08:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括旅館在内的整個滑雪場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.40,0:08:05.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都由緋之宮度假區交予二穗小姐經營了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.11,0:08:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠水說的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.87,0:08:09.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是二穗嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是幫大忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這倒沒什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.16,0:08:15.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是雪人必須要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.17,0:08:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們要是發現了告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.54,0:08:19.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到時定有重謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.79,0:08:20.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重謝?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.88,0:08:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二穗小姐爲了尋找雪人發佈了巨額賞金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.93,0:08:28.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二穗 是時候上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.97,0:08:32.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 你們來即是客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.06,0:08:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會好好款待你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.31,0:08:37.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡情享受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.45,0:08:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是店主特供的木船拼盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.00,0:08:59.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是店主特供的日本牛排
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.51,0:09:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是店主推薦的炒麵麵包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木船拼盤真好吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.02,0:09:14.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.39,0:09:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這份款待心意我已經切身體會到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用肚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.65,0:09:23.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被子已經鋪好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.24,0:09:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真名要睡在伊緒旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.40,0:09:29.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是隨意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.33,0:09:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛出爐的咖喱麵包一樣的觸感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.12,0:09:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像聼懂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聼懂了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.96,0:09:46.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天伊緒和椿芽也一起去找雪人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.63,0:09:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 我們也要去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.13,0:09:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這有什麽 一起去嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.47,0:09:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 伊緒決定參加了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.68,0:09:59.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,椿芽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.02,0:10:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也參加吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.48,0:10:03.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有點興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.02,0:10:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.28,0:10:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天就叫Altair·Torte探險隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.36,0:10:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把雪人找出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入了兩個新伙伴后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.96,0:10:24.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入了兩個新伙伴后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.59,0:10:27.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爲了搜尋未知生物雪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.05,0:10:30.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們繼續向著深山進發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.34,0:10:35.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山尻浩史探險隊好像的確是這個樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.60,0:10:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到居然再現了攝像和解說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊好像有什麽動靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.06,0:10:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在這時 真名隊長好像發現了什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.28,0:10:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像真的有什麽東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.86,0:10:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有三個 雪人親~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.37,0:10:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.32,0:10:57.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會是熊吧 太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.04,0:10:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.12,0:11:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們探險隊終於遇到了傳說中的雪人了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.76,0:11:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真名 找到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.30,0:11:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.22,0:11:20.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很危險的啊 要是熊怎麽辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.60,0:11:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 那是雪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.31,0:11:25.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪人也很危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.69,0:11:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行事要小心一點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 什麽也看不到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.49,0:11:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看錯了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.86,0:11:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好看錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.74,0:11:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.67,0:11:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餓死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.97,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅羅?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.36,0:12:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿成這樣 食物也不帶就進入雪山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來想馬上返回的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.11,0:12:17.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爲什麽會來這兒呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.28,0:12:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說抓到雪人就能得到巨額賞金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.50,0:12:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然陽奈反對的說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.17,0:12:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先看一下雪人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.46,0:12:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是什麽大山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.59,0:12:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以爲大致繞一圈就能找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.92,0:12:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果完全沒有發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.55,0:12:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就遇難了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.89,0:12:38.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回程我們還是記得的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.05,0:12:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,途中發現了不像是熊的巨大脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.73,0:12:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是和真名找到的脚印一樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 應該是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.90,0:12:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後追著那串脚印進入了一個洞穴后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一隻熊在裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.86,0:12:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驚慌失措逃跑的時候遇難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.57,0:13:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是熊的錯 錯在驚擾它的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.66,0:13:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽果然那串脚印是那頭熊的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.75,0:13:10.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那不是熊的脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.30,0:13:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Sirius
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.26,0:13:18.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們還應該記得吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.72,0:13:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅羅 陽奈 還有小織
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.81,0:13:23.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這附近遇難了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.77,0:13:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 找了雪人的綫索了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.65,0:13:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅羅她們發現雪人的足跡進入了一個洞穴中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.19,0:13:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.90,0:13:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在洞穴裏遇到了一頭熊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.74,0:13:42.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懷疑會不會是熊的脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.91,0:13:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個洞穴在哪兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.04,0:13:48.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往那邊一直走 就在山脊的背面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.34,0:13:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們相信我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.22,0:14:00.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算真的是熊 畢竟也是在我家滑雪場附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.22,0:14:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必須做好應對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.10,0:14:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也能跟著去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.02,0:14:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們也一起...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.69,0:14:10.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿成這樣跟來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.81,0:14:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萬一遇上暴風雪我們也救不了你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.15,0:14:13.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們才不需要你幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛不就差點遇難了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.24,0:14:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們趕快給我下山去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.20,0:14:31.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二穗 帶紅羅她們過來不也挺好的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.96,0:14:33.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪山上可沒這麽簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.21,0:14:38.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我暫時還不相信她們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.34,0:14:42.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是因爲被摩根娜控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前段時間也還是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.89,0:14:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,紅羅她們已經不是敵人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.77,0:14:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.35,0:14:54.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不想和還不完全信任的人一起玩火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.94,0:14:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看清她們的本質是需要時間的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.32,0:15:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有句話叫 千里之堤毀於蟻穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.95,0:15:05.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說螞蟻可以舉起相當於自身體重50倍的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.33,0:15:08.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這應該沒什麽聯係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.71,0:15:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到附近居然有這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.17,0:15:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這入口看上去好有感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.01,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始興奮起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.43,0:15:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們終於進入了有雪人出沒的洞穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.94,0:15:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種神秘生物真的會出現嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.19,0:15:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在做什麽呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.65,0:15:43.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.57,0:15:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山尻浩史探險隊對嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.16,0:15:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.33,0:15:49.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很喜歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二穗也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.29,0:15:56.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是被你強行拉過去一起看而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.38,0:15:59.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像還買了盒裝全集
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.96,0:16:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.92,0:16:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還算是有趣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得那是限量生產的吧 好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.89,0:16:11.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次借給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.94,0:16:14.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二穗小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.86,0:16:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊有什麽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 那是妖魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.29,0:16:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 妖魔?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.04,0:16:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先等一下 這不是很糟糕嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.17,0:16:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 還沒有聽說過妖魔出現在現實世界的案例
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.13,0:16:45.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.47,0:16:47.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果妖魔暴露在公衆面前的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.68,0:16:49.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果那是妖魔的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.10,0:16:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有裝備我們打不過啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.68,0:16:55.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是必須在妖魔逃走之前...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.27,0:16:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得想點辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.61,0:17:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 是這麽回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些水晶恐怕就是斯特拉水晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.16,0:17:15.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是擁有相同特性的物質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.87,0:17:21.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖魔通過這個從五次元時空來到這個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.92,0:17:22.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們追上去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.92,0:17:25.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了五次元時空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.51,0:17:27.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提耶菈老師就能給我們傳送裝備了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.97,0:17:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊 好主意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.60,0:17:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我們上吧 Altair·Torte探險隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.72,0:17:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Biscuit·Sirius也出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.69,0:17:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現實世界的確存在誕生斯特拉水晶類似物質的可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.98,0:17:49.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖魔可能會憑藉此物來到現實世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.61,0:17:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會在這兒阻止它 請立刻傳送裝備過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.45,0:17:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 服務器出現了故障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.70,0:17:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Biscuit·Sirius的裝備支援會遲到一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.17,0:18:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情況很糟糕 正在搶修
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.17,0:18:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麽 那Altair·Torte的裝備呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.47,0:18:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麽快給Altair·Torte傳送裝備
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.05,0:18:14.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 Altair·Torte也在那兒嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.43,0:18:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.48,0:18:25.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聼好了 我們的裝備由於服務器搶修暫時不能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.28,0:18:29.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對付妖魔就交給Altair·Torte了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.45,0:18:31.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.03,0:18:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Altair·Torte探險隊終於進入高潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經過了約1小時45分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.29,0:18:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她們沒問題吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.35,0:18:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能交給她們了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.14,0:18:59.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且她們配合比之前要精煉多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.35,0:19:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過還是有很多瑕疵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.44,0:19:10.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然談不上顯著 但的確在成長著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.12,0:19:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不止一隻嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.51,0:19:36.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.89,0:19:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麽會在這兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.85,0:19:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那麽下山太沒面子了 所以就追過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.94,0:19:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來雪人的真相就是這家夥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.95,0:19:57.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個 非常感謝你們搭救二穗小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.37,0:20:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麽大不了的 不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.29,0:20:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.68,0:20:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛剛那場戰鬥大家沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.68,0:20:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 虛驚一場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.35,0:20:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欸 紅羅她們人呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.65,0:20:27.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.98,0:20:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 雪人的真面目居然是妖魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 給人添麻煩也要有個限度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.40,0:20:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 這樣就能作爲滑雪場的招牌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖魔可不能公開出來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.66,0:20:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說 雪人周邊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部作廢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.00,0:20:50.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒辦法 只能想別的辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人挺有意思的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.72,0:20:58.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都在一個學校 要不要和她們做朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.39,0:21:00.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不很好嗎
